@startuml sequence_sse_realtime
!theme plain

title Real-time Dashboard Updates via SSE

actor "DevOps Engineer" as User
participant "Web Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "API Server" as API
database "TimescaleDB" as DB

User -> Dashboard : Opens dashboard
Dashboard -> API : GET /api/v1/stream (SSE)
activate API

loop On new metrics
    API -> DB : Query latest metrics
    API --> Dashboard : SSE event (metric data)
    Dashboard -> Dashboard : Update visualizations
end

note right of API : Connection stays open\nServer pushes updates

@enduml